1
00:00:02,400 --> 00:00:04,499
(Previously) If Your Highness
has really forgotten everything...

2
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:05,999
shall I help refresh your memory?

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:07,761
No matter what, you
must not soften your heart.

4
00:00:07,785 --> 00:00:10,799
We still need information
from Prince Thin. Understood?

5
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:12,800
You met with Prince Thin?

6
00:00:14,200 --> 00:00:16,337
My people suspect that
Phob might be involved in the

7
00:00:16,361 --> 00:00:18,499
movement planning to
change the government system.

8
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:19,500
Is that true, Dad?

9
00:00:19,900 --> 00:00:22,176
Did Your Highness come to observe
the field training yourself?

10
00:00:22,200 --> 00:00:27,200
I must inspect to ensure order, just in
case someone is planning to cause trouble.

11
00:01:50,500 --> 00:01:56,500
"The Edge of Horizon"
(Episode 5)

12
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:00,501
Mr. Phobthee.

13
00:02:01,247 --> 00:02:02,248
Mr. Phobthee!

14
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:04,080
Phob!

15
00:02:09,388 --> 00:02:10,404
What is it?

16
00:02:10,935 --> 00:02:13,284
- Did you hear what you just said?
- It was the truth.

17
00:02:14,136 --> 00:02:16,884
The economy is going downhill
and people are struggling.

18
00:02:17,146 --> 00:02:19,284
Instead, aristocrats do nothing about it.

19
00:02:19,315 --> 00:02:21,204
Everyone is trying to save the country.

20
00:02:21,244 --> 00:02:22,444
That is from your perspective.

21
00:02:22,924 --> 00:02:24,044
But in my perspective,

22
00:02:24,374 --> 00:02:25,804
it should have been done better,

23
00:02:26,082 --> 00:02:27,459
not waiting until people
are dying from starvation.

24
00:02:27,483 --> 00:02:28,484
You need to stop talking!

25
00:02:28,492 --> 00:02:30,169
You do know that people
could misunderstand you

26
00:02:30,193 --> 00:02:31,560
if they just hear what you said, don't you?

27
00:02:31,584 --> 00:02:33,084
You could be in danger.

28
00:02:36,007 --> 00:02:37,008
Why are you smiling?

29
00:02:41,452 --> 00:02:42,453
Hey,

30
00:02:43,418 --> 00:02:45,084
do you care about me?

31
00:02:46,252 --> 00:02:47,324
As a colleague.

32
00:02:53,068 --> 00:02:54,324
Right,

33
00:02:55,316 --> 00:02:58,596
I haven't received the schedule of royal
family members who will attend the event.

34
00:02:59,124 --> 00:03:00,284
Where are they staying at?

35
00:03:01,494 --> 00:03:02,964
I can provide them protection.

36
00:03:04,594 --> 00:03:07,084
I told you that it wasn't your job.

37
00:03:31,658 --> 00:03:34,154
I saw the reaction of Kitti and Phob today,

38
00:03:34,244 --> 00:03:35,944
it was obvious of what they had in mind.

39
00:03:37,738 --> 00:03:41,004
They could be planning
for a regime change.

40
00:03:44,504 --> 00:03:45,505
Dad?

41
00:03:46,132 --> 00:03:47,133
Actually,

42
00:03:48,207 --> 00:03:49,924
Phob asked me

43
00:03:50,164 --> 00:03:52,365
about the schedule for
all royal family members.

44
00:03:53,119 --> 00:03:54,120
He did?

45
00:03:55,463 --> 00:03:56,644
Did you give it to him?

46
00:03:57,704 --> 00:03:58,705
I haven't.

47
00:03:59,064 --> 00:04:00,644
It wasn't his job.

48
00:04:02,324 --> 00:04:03,364
But Dad,

49
00:04:04,404 --> 00:04:07,605
I think perhaps he just felt oppressed

50
00:04:08,964 --> 00:04:11,124
that the country was in trouble,

51
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,840
we're facing economic recession,

52
00:04:14,284 --> 00:04:17,204
I don't think he would do such thing.

53
00:04:24,252 --> 00:04:25,253
Tin,

54
00:04:26,780 --> 00:04:28,084
I need your help.

55
00:04:29,744 --> 00:04:30,745
Okay?

56
00:04:34,652 --> 00:04:36,404
The regime change?

57
00:04:39,064 --> 00:04:41,844
You dream big, you filthy slave.

58
00:04:46,468 --> 00:04:48,724
Do you remember our conversation

59
00:04:48,762 --> 00:04:50,644
before you left to study in the UK?

60
00:04:51,876 --> 00:04:53,364
Before I left for the UK?

61
00:04:54,842 --> 00:04:56,444
Before you left,

62
00:04:56,591 --> 00:05:00,164
you said that you'd talk to
our fathers about our marriage.

63
00:05:00,655 --> 00:05:02,204
I remember it well.

64
00:05:03,322 --> 00:05:04,559
I remember it, too.

65
00:05:05,722 --> 00:05:07,684
If you don't want to marry me…

66
00:05:07,823 --> 00:05:10,004
You don't want to marry me either.

67
00:05:11,564 --> 00:05:12,644
I know

68
00:05:13,143 --> 00:05:14,844
that you don't love me.

69
00:05:15,090 --> 00:05:17,004
You love someone else.

70
00:05:23,463 --> 00:05:24,464
I'm sorry.

71
00:05:25,404 --> 00:05:27,204
You don't need to apologize.

72
00:05:28,047 --> 00:05:30,048
We don't love each other like that

73
00:05:30,518 --> 00:05:33,230
and we shouldn't be bound by marriage.

74
00:05:34,004 --> 00:05:35,605
The problem is that.

75
00:05:36,044 --> 00:05:38,644
I can't talk about this topic to my dad.

76
00:05:38,943 --> 00:05:40,604
He never listens to me.

77
00:05:43,004 --> 00:05:44,644
I understand.

78
00:05:46,257 --> 00:05:49,617
I will talk to my dad and
our elderly relatives about this.

79
00:05:54,548 --> 00:05:55,549
Tin,

80
00:05:56,122 --> 00:05:58,764
even though we wont' be engaged anymore,

81
00:05:59,946 --> 00:06:04,044
I still love and care for you.

82
00:06:04,852 --> 00:06:07,404
If something is bothering you,

83
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:09,164
whatever it is,

84
00:06:09,684 --> 00:06:11,844
please know that I will
always be here for you.

85
00:06:11,903 --> 00:06:13,964
I will listen and help you through it.

86
00:06:14,799 --> 00:06:16,564
Thank you, Siri.

87
00:06:17,204 --> 00:06:19,544
I'm so lucky to have
you as a lovely sister,

88
00:06:19,759 --> 00:06:22,124
who always means well and understands me.

89
00:06:26,642 --> 00:06:27,643
Hi, Phob.

90
00:06:29,236 --> 00:06:30,237
Janthorn.

91
00:06:31,039 --> 00:06:32,684
Are you here for a garden festival?

92
00:06:33,412 --> 00:06:35,844
That's right, I want to put it in the news

93
00:06:35,948 --> 00:06:37,604
so I asked Phob to take me here.

94
00:06:47,442 --> 00:06:49,684
Phob, please take care of Tin.

95
00:07:18,044 --> 00:07:19,045
Follow me.

96
00:07:32,935 --> 00:07:35,244
You look so happy today.

97
00:07:35,884 --> 00:07:37,604
Unlike the other day, you looked so gloomy.

98
00:07:38,604 --> 00:07:41,004
I'm happy because of you,

99
00:07:41,050 --> 00:07:42,604
for giving me advice the other day.

100
00:07:44,866 --> 00:07:45,867
Wait,

101
00:07:47,490 --> 00:07:48,762
I thought a friend of your friend

102
00:07:48,786 --> 00:07:51,244
had that problem.

103
00:07:51,980 --> 00:07:55,684
Well, a friend of my friend wanted to say
thank you to you.

104
00:08:13,823 --> 00:08:16,884
Have some cake, it's delicious.

105
00:09:12,184 --> 00:09:13,185
How is it? Delicious?

106
00:09:15,844 --> 00:09:16,845
Yeah.

107
00:09:21,335 --> 00:09:22,964
Why are you leading me here?

108
00:09:27,210 --> 00:09:28,484
What do you want?

109
00:09:32,164 --> 00:09:33,524
What are you doing?

110
00:09:33,892 --> 00:09:36,051
What? You asked me about what I wanted.

111
00:09:36,618 --> 00:09:38,164
This is what I want.

112
00:09:38,540 --> 00:09:40,204
Not this.

113
00:09:46,514 --> 00:09:47,515
It's about this.

114
00:09:52,314 --> 00:09:53,844
A schedule for when

115
00:09:53,915 --> 00:09:56,275
all the royal family members'
arrive during the celebration.

116
00:10:01,842 --> 00:10:03,324
Why did you change your mind?

117
00:10:04,524 --> 00:10:06,764
You said that you wanted
it for protection plan.

118
00:10:08,740 --> 00:10:10,604
Now that I gave it to you, it'd be over.

119
00:10:11,647 --> 00:10:13,844
And you should stop messing
around with me already.

120
00:10:33,351 --> 00:10:34,352
Phob!

121
00:10:37,164 --> 00:10:38,165
Prince Chatthorn?

122
00:10:41,794 --> 00:10:44,004
Oh, you still remember me?

123
00:10:44,795 --> 00:10:46,235
I thought you would forget about me.

124
00:10:54,359 --> 00:10:56,124
You're a Captain's mom now.

125
00:10:57,708 --> 00:10:59,724
And you might forget who you used to be.

126
00:11:01,690 --> 00:11:05,284
I'm grateful for all of your family
members, I never forgot any of you.

127
00:11:08,063 --> 00:11:09,484
You never forgot?

128
00:11:12,143 --> 00:11:15,644
Why was your son

129
00:11:16,511 --> 00:11:18,884
so ungrateful to all of us?

130
00:11:20,710 --> 00:11:23,350
He is trying to destroy the pride
and honor of me and my people.

131
00:11:24,364 --> 00:11:25,684
What do you mean by that?

132
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:27,804
What did Phob do?

133
00:11:31,204 --> 00:11:32,388
How could you ask me that?

134
00:11:32,488 --> 00:11:35,684
- Your son…
- You found out about Phob and your brother?

135
00:11:38,522 --> 00:11:39,523
Huh?

136
00:11:40,239 --> 00:11:41,240
Phob?

137
00:11:41,450 --> 00:11:42,451
And Tinnakorn?

138
00:11:45,994 --> 00:11:47,884
I tried to stop my son

139
00:11:48,495 --> 00:11:50,124
from being around Prince Tinnakorn.

140
00:11:51,364 --> 00:11:53,524
He could've tainted the prince's reputation.

141
00:11:57,204 --> 00:11:58,724
What did he to to my brother?

142
00:12:03,164 --> 00:12:04,404
What did he to to my brother?

143
00:12:05,124 --> 00:12:06,604
What did he to to my brother?

144
00:12:07,546 --> 00:12:09,810
He did something to Tin that night,
didn't he? What did he do?

145
00:12:09,833 --> 00:12:12,243
What did he do? What did he do to Tin?

146
00:12:12,268 --> 00:12:15,204
Tell me! I said tell me! Come on!

147
00:12:15,269 --> 00:12:17,124
Let her go! What are you doing to my mom?

148
00:12:17,924 --> 00:12:18,964
Phob!

149
00:12:20,463 --> 00:12:21,724
Mom!

150
00:12:22,474 --> 00:12:23,475
Mom!

151
00:12:25,300 --> 00:12:26,301
Mom!

152
00:12:27,460 --> 00:12:28,461
Mom!

153
00:12:28,788 --> 00:12:30,404
You took care of what I asked, right?

154
00:12:32,404 --> 00:12:33,405
I did.

155
00:12:35,682 --> 00:12:37,944
If he is a part of the rebellion,

156
00:12:38,834 --> 00:12:40,844
we will find out that day.

157
00:12:46,908 --> 00:12:47,909
Dad!

158
00:12:50,178 --> 00:12:53,124
About Phob's big attempt
to transform the nation,

159
00:12:54,164 --> 00:12:56,124
don't you worry a thing.

160
00:12:56,487 --> 00:12:57,944
I handled it already.

161
00:12:58,064 --> 00:12:59,184
How did you know about it?

162
00:13:00,316 --> 00:13:01,317
What did you handle?

163
00:13:01,679 --> 00:13:04,166
I heard about what you and Tin said,

164
00:13:04,463 --> 00:13:06,594
so I threatened Nual and she passed out.

165
00:13:06,746 --> 00:13:09,004
- I don't think he would…
- How much did you said to her?

166
00:13:10,764 --> 00:13:13,084
I didn't say anything
much, she just passed out…

167
00:13:14,540 --> 00:13:15,341
Chat!

168
00:13:15,404 --> 00:13:17,644
You're not helping and
you're causing more troubles!

169
00:13:18,283 --> 00:13:20,117
You're so good at stupid things!

170
00:13:21,794 --> 00:13:24,844
Why did you hit me? I
was just trying to help.

171
00:13:25,111 --> 00:13:26,204
You? Helping?

172
00:13:26,279 --> 00:13:28,644
If you hadn't done anything,

173
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:30,204
it would have been better for us.

174
00:13:30,405 --> 00:13:32,117
Now they know about the plan

175
00:13:32,239 --> 00:13:34,284
and it was all ruined because of you.

176
00:13:35,684 --> 00:13:37,044
I started to wonder

177
00:13:37,098 --> 00:13:38,764
if you really are my son.

178
00:13:39,124 --> 00:13:41,604
Or someone switched
you at birth with a calf!

179
00:13:41,639 --> 00:13:43,204
That's why you're so stupid like this!

180
00:13:45,020 --> 00:13:47,124
Get the hell out of my face! Go!

181
00:13:47,287 --> 00:13:48,967
I don't want to see your face anymore. Go!

182
00:13:49,844 --> 00:13:50,845
Chat.

183
00:14:08,015 --> 00:14:09,016
Chat.

184
00:14:11,644 --> 00:14:14,364
Dad is still furious, please
don't be mad at him.

185
00:14:18,404 --> 00:14:19,818
How could someone like me

186
00:14:21,871 --> 00:14:23,324
be mad at anyone?

187
00:14:24,138 --> 00:14:25,139
Chat.

188
00:14:30,204 --> 00:14:32,444
I'm stupid like a buffalo.

189
00:14:33,698 --> 00:14:35,218
I shouldn't have been born as his son.

190
00:14:51,818 --> 00:14:52,749
But...

191
00:14:52,769 --> 00:14:54,826
you shouldn't have hurt Nual like that.

192
00:14:56,900 --> 00:14:58,490
You would just make it worse.

193
00:15:00,058 --> 00:15:02,204
Are you blaming me even more?

194
00:15:07,191 --> 00:15:08,192
That's right.

195
00:15:09,090 --> 00:15:10,091
I'm not you.

196
00:15:11,444 --> 00:15:12,644
- No!
- I did everything wrong.

197
00:15:15,311 --> 00:15:16,404
Since I was young,

198
00:15:19,332 --> 00:15:20,684
I can never be good at anything.

199
00:15:23,404 --> 00:15:24,804
I wasn't a good student.

200
00:15:27,735 --> 00:15:29,364
I couldn't be as good as you were.

201
00:15:36,642 --> 00:15:37,643
Do you know

202
00:15:39,450 --> 00:15:41,451
how jealous I am of you?

203
00:15:43,690 --> 00:15:46,044
Dad loves only you,

204
00:15:47,466 --> 00:15:48,884
he praises only you.

205
00:15:53,903 --> 00:15:54,964
And me…

206
00:15:57,444 --> 00:15:58,524
I'm not good at anything.

207
00:15:59,164 --> 00:16:01,044
Stop talking like that.

208
00:16:03,524 --> 00:16:04,844
Don't ever think like that.

209
00:16:05,984 --> 00:16:07,044
Stop thinking like that.

210
00:16:09,037 --> 00:16:10,757
You're also his son.

211
00:16:11,972 --> 00:16:13,164
Dad loves you.

212
00:16:14,404 --> 00:16:15,684
Dad loves you, okay?

213
00:16:15,724 --> 00:16:16,725
Not true.

214
00:16:18,544 --> 00:16:20,245
Trust me, he loves you.

215
00:16:22,250 --> 00:16:23,264
And I love you.

216
00:16:28,260 --> 00:16:29,284
You hear me?

217
00:16:30,084 --> 00:16:33,004
Dad loves you, I love you,
everyone in this house loves you.

218
00:16:35,404 --> 00:16:36,605
We all love you.

219
00:16:44,535 --> 00:16:45,536
You understand?

220
00:16:48,791 --> 00:16:51,151
If you're not going to stop
crying, I will tell Ruethaisiri.

221
00:16:51,724 --> 00:16:52,725
Will you stop crying?

222
00:16:57,373 --> 00:16:58,374
Good boy.

223
00:17:08,442 --> 00:17:10,844
She has suffered from heart disease.

224
00:17:11,247 --> 00:17:12,964
When she is terrifed over something,

225
00:17:13,159 --> 00:17:15,644
her heart works harder than usual.

226
00:17:16,023 --> 00:17:17,204
And it is dangerous.

227
00:17:18,151 --> 00:17:21,324
I'd suggest her to rest

228
00:17:21,764 --> 00:17:24,164
and avoid hearing news
that could upset her.

229
00:17:27,823 --> 00:17:28,824
I understand.

230
00:17:29,543 --> 00:17:30,544
Thank you.

231
00:18:08,522 --> 00:18:09,884
What the hell is wrong with you?

232
00:18:10,407 --> 00:18:11,447
- Huh?
- What do you think?

233
00:18:14,316 --> 00:18:17,164
Do you know who I am? Do you?

234
00:18:17,644 --> 00:18:19,004
You're Prince Chatthorn.

235
00:18:37,922 --> 00:18:39,164
That's enough.

236
00:18:42,463 --> 00:18:43,484
Stop it.

237
00:18:56,360 --> 00:18:57,361
Phob?

238
00:18:59,482 --> 00:19:00,564
You slave!

239
00:19:01,615 --> 00:19:03,164
How dare you do this to me?

240
00:19:05,524 --> 00:19:06,525
What did I do?

241
00:19:09,284 --> 00:19:11,444
I'm here to help you.

242
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:19,284
What are you standing here for?

243
00:19:22,340 --> 00:19:23,444
I'm sorry.

244
00:19:24,783 --> 00:19:25,784
Please go.

245
00:19:36,399 --> 00:19:37,400
See?

246
00:19:38,244 --> 00:19:39,844
I'm here to help you, really.

247
00:19:43,504 --> 00:19:44,505
Therefore,

248
00:19:45,724 --> 00:19:46,725
from now on,

249
00:19:48,114 --> 00:19:49,644
you need to behave, okay?

250
00:19:55,644 --> 00:19:57,645
Don't mess with my mom ever again.

251
00:20:09,124 --> 00:20:10,125
Come on.

252
00:20:58,610 --> 00:21:00,604
Nual! Pleae don't get up, please.

253
00:21:01,191 --> 00:21:02,192
Prince Tinnakorn?

254
00:21:06,196 --> 00:21:07,674
Nual, I…

255
00:21:09,524 --> 00:21:10,524
I'm here to apologize.

256
00:21:12,684 --> 00:21:14,564
I'm apologizing for my brother.

257
00:21:15,796 --> 00:21:16,924
I'm really sorry.

258
00:21:16,991 --> 00:21:18,364
Your Highness,

259
00:21:19,322 --> 00:21:22,284
please don't do that, please?

260
00:21:27,498 --> 00:21:28,564
Did my brother

261
00:21:30,016 --> 00:21:31,490
say anything to you?

262
00:21:35,804 --> 00:21:38,244
He said that.

263
00:21:39,544 --> 00:21:40,545
Phob was likely

264
00:21:41,975 --> 00:21:43,844
to ruin your reputation.

265
00:21:45,327 --> 00:21:47,364
Did he know about this?

266
00:21:47,951 --> 00:21:48,952
No, he didn't.

267
00:21:50,186 --> 00:21:51,187
It's not that.

268
00:21:53,647 --> 00:21:55,284
About that,

269
00:21:56,202 --> 00:21:57,724
besides about Phob and I,

270
00:21:58,684 --> 00:22:00,364
did he say something else?

271
00:22:01,885 --> 00:22:03,164
Something like...

272
00:22:04,524 --> 00:22:05,804
about Phob's work?

273
00:22:06,644 --> 00:22:07,645
Or

274
00:22:08,386 --> 00:22:10,744
what his plan is?

275
00:22:12,604 --> 00:22:13,724
Did he say anything?

276
00:22:15,964 --> 00:22:17,044
No, I don't think so.

277
00:22:23,660 --> 00:22:24,804
Your Highness,

278
00:22:26,284 --> 00:22:27,285
from now on,

279
00:22:28,524 --> 00:22:29,964
I will stop my son

280
00:22:30,684 --> 00:22:33,124
not to be around you anymore.

281
00:22:34,284 --> 00:22:35,844
It is entirely my son's fault

282
00:22:36,244 --> 00:22:38,445
to cause all the mess.

283
00:22:39,220 --> 00:22:42,484
He was ungrateful to your family.

284
00:22:43,358 --> 00:22:45,603
Instead, he tried to

285
00:22:46,064 --> 00:22:48,484
- ruin your reputation.
- It's not his fault.

286
00:22:48,815 --> 00:22:50,964
Not true. It is his fault.

287
00:22:52,004 --> 00:22:53,484
It is Phob's fault.

288
00:22:54,372 --> 00:22:57,450
He dragged the sky down to stoop to his level.

289
00:22:58,351 --> 00:23:00,544
He tried to run away from me.

290
00:23:02,138 --> 00:23:03,364
He really did.

291
00:23:09,258 --> 00:23:10,259
It was me.

292
00:23:10,922 --> 00:23:12,644
I pulled him closer to me.

293
00:23:17,044 --> 00:23:19,645
And it was me who left him.

294
00:23:24,799 --> 00:23:26,964
I caused you and Phob to leave the palace.

295
00:23:27,983 --> 00:23:31,044
I pushed both of you to struggle in life.

296
00:23:32,055 --> 00:23:34,604
I'm sorry. Please don't be mad at me.

297
00:23:34,716 --> 00:23:38,124
Oh my goodness, please don't say that.

298
00:23:39,684 --> 00:23:40,685
You know what?

299
00:23:41,900 --> 00:23:46,444
When I saw that Phob became
Captain, I was so happy for him.

300
00:23:48,359 --> 00:23:49,924
I was happy to see that

301
00:23:51,132 --> 00:23:52,772
he was the same talented man that I knew.

302
00:23:56,517 --> 00:23:59,537
When I learned that
after he left the palace,

303
00:24:01,125 --> 00:24:02,884
he struggled so much in his life.

304
00:24:05,324 --> 00:24:06,806
I wanted to praise him

305
00:24:07,925 --> 00:24:10,284
for his effort that he refused to give up.

306
00:24:12,884 --> 00:24:15,604
He is a soldier with bright future.

307
00:24:16,885 --> 00:24:19,404
I will never cause him any damage.

308
00:24:21,855 --> 00:24:23,044
I will never let him

309
00:24:25,124 --> 00:24:27,164
ruin his future because of me.

310
00:25:02,020 --> 00:25:04,724
My sources received
the schedule of royal family members

311
00:25:05,412 --> 00:25:07,324
and it is the same
information that you got.

312
00:25:07,583 --> 00:25:10,031
It is trustworthy.

313
00:25:11,087 --> 00:25:13,607
The royal ceremony will take place
in the first couple of days.

314
00:25:15,076 --> 00:25:18,084
I think we should start
our plan the next day

315
00:25:19,244 --> 00:25:21,884
when they arrive and
gather up at the theater,

316
00:25:22,964 --> 00:25:24,404
according to their schedule.

317
00:25:25,564 --> 00:25:27,565
It will be easier to control them.

318
00:25:27,839 --> 00:25:28,840
I agree with your plan.

319
00:25:29,551 --> 00:25:32,524
Phobthee, you need to
lead our team there

320
00:25:33,215 --> 00:25:35,964
and detain important
members for negotiation.

321
00:25:42,013 --> 00:25:44,294
There will be no royal family
members staying there.

322
00:25:45,404 --> 00:25:48,484
Our people will stay
there and wait for the fight

323
00:25:48,604 --> 00:25:50,044
against the ungrateful traitors.

324
00:25:50,970 --> 00:25:52,524
We are digging up the pond

325
00:25:53,724 --> 00:25:55,724
and now we are waiting
for fish to catch its bait.

326
00:26:36,988 --> 00:26:38,735
The royal ceremony in
the first couples of days

327
00:26:38,759 --> 00:26:41,124
turned out to be so
marvelous, Your Highness.

328
00:26:41,978 --> 00:26:44,098
People looked so happy and
they enjoyed the ceremony.

329
00:26:46,714 --> 00:26:48,724
I hope it stays this way until the end.

330
00:26:53,082 --> 00:26:55,564
Did you hear what the
King said the other day?

331
00:26:57,396 --> 00:27:00,684
When people are happy in the country,

332
00:27:01,794 --> 00:27:04,324
the country will remain in peace.

333
00:27:06,252 --> 00:27:07,564
Our country

334
00:27:07,908 --> 00:27:10,924
has been a peaceful nation for 150 years.

335
00:27:13,009 --> 00:27:16,684
I hope that Siamese people will continue to
live happily like this forever,

336
00:27:18,156 --> 00:27:20,884
with no traitors to ruin
the peace of the nation.

337
00:27:51,133 --> 00:27:53,623
The important members are
gathered up in one place, right?

338
00:27:55,084 --> 00:27:56,085
Yes, sir.

339
00:27:56,690 --> 00:27:59,284
My sources reported that
if they'd start the mission,

340
00:27:59,602 --> 00:28:01,682
they would send someone
to detain our members first.

341
00:28:01,714 --> 00:28:02,850
If that's the case,

342
00:28:03,191 --> 00:28:05,284
the leader should be a
person who is close to Kitti,

343
00:28:05,871 --> 00:28:06,872
Captain Phobthee.

344
00:28:08,965 --> 00:28:11,724
If they break in, you can shoot them all.

345
00:28:19,260 --> 00:28:20,261
Dad?

346
00:28:20,883 --> 00:28:22,644
That's not what you said to me.

347
00:28:23,470 --> 00:28:27,110
You said that if Phob was
involved with this, you'd get him out

348
00:28:27,154 --> 00:28:28,155
and you'd help him.

349
00:28:28,544 --> 00:28:31,364
If he started it, I needed to kill him.

350
00:28:32,696 --> 00:28:35,724
Tin, you can't go soft on him.

351
00:29:47,287 --> 00:29:49,568
When you reach the destination,
tell them to let me know.

352
00:30:00,226 --> 00:30:01,227
Excuse me,

353
00:30:01,724 --> 00:30:03,004
did you see Capt. Phobthee?

354
00:30:03,944 --> 00:30:06,124
He led the soldiers
out of this place already.

355
00:30:08,564 --> 00:30:09,764
- He's gone?
- Yes, sir.

356
00:30:25,572 --> 00:30:26,573
Phob!

357
00:30:27,556 --> 00:30:28,557
Phob!

358
00:30:29,663 --> 00:30:30,664
Phob!

359
00:30:35,002 --> 00:30:36,003
Phob!

360
00:30:38,778 --> 00:30:41,564
If they break in, you can shoot them all.

361
00:30:53,767 --> 00:30:54,924
Phob!

362
00:30:56,484 --> 00:30:57,485
Phob!

363
00:31:16,730 --> 00:31:17,731
Your Highness?

364
00:31:23,844 --> 00:31:24,845
Phob.

365
00:31:26,044 --> 00:31:27,045
Phob.

366
00:31:33,324 --> 00:31:34,524
Are you okay?

367
00:31:35,388 --> 00:31:37,884
You didn't ride in the
car with the soldiers?

368
00:31:42,698 --> 00:31:45,564
They're done for the day

369
00:31:46,575 --> 00:31:48,295
so they are travelling back to their camps.

370
00:31:49,407 --> 00:31:53,124
What about the protection
for aristocrats at the theatre?

371
00:31:53,524 --> 00:31:55,404
You didn't do it?

372
00:31:56,604 --> 00:31:57,734
About the security plan,

373
00:32:02,127 --> 00:32:04,244
the civil officials all agreed that

374
00:32:04,452 --> 00:32:07,084
we should postpone our
mission, not to do it today.

375
00:32:08,044 --> 00:32:09,964
There are many people
attending the celebration.

376
00:32:10,364 --> 00:32:11,924
It could lead to a bloodbath situation.

377
00:32:12,144 --> 00:32:13,924
I'll tell them to abort the mission.

378
00:32:37,940 --> 00:32:40,284
The Royal Guard has
taken over the protection.

379
00:32:45,148 --> 00:32:46,149
It's okay.

380
00:32:48,295 --> 00:32:49,296
It's alright.

381
00:32:50,244 --> 00:32:51,245
I am here with you.

382
00:33:02,924 --> 00:33:04,444
I thought I would never see you again.

383
00:33:14,095 --> 00:33:15,096
Phob!

384
00:33:15,192 --> 00:33:17,244
Phob, you slave!

385
00:33:17,407 --> 00:33:18,564
Go to hell!

386
00:33:18,892 --> 00:33:19,893
Phob!

387
00:33:27,820 --> 00:33:29,380
Your Highness!

388
00:33:30,484 --> 00:33:31,485
Your Highness!

389
00:33:35,610 --> 00:33:37,924
Your Highness!

390
00:33:38,794 --> 00:33:39,795
Your Highness!

391
00:33:39,804 --> 00:33:40,924
Phob, are you okay?

392
00:33:50,644 --> 00:33:51,645
Your Highness!

393
00:33:52,404 --> 00:33:53,405
Your Highness!

394
00:33:54,620 --> 00:33:55,621
Your Highness!

395
00:33:59,359 --> 00:34:01,164
I am not dreaming, am I?

396
00:34:02,460 --> 00:34:03,464
You are dreaming

397
00:34:06,588 --> 00:34:07,724
and you will wake up soon.

398
00:34:53,340 --> 00:34:54,844
Chat is here.

399
00:34:54,940 --> 00:34:57,404
When will Tin be back?

400
00:34:58,364 --> 00:34:59,365
I don't know either.

401
00:34:59,804 --> 00:35:00,844
It is getting late.

402
00:35:01,564 --> 00:35:04,444
I haven't seen him since after the
ceremony. I didn't know where he was.

403
00:35:17,394 --> 00:35:19,395
[Operating Room]

404
00:35:30,394 --> 00:35:31,524
How is he?

405
00:35:31,828 --> 00:35:33,244
He is doing fine.

406
00:35:33,583 --> 00:35:35,463
The bullet grazed his
arm, it wasn't lodged in.

407
00:35:35,637 --> 00:35:37,370
I healed his wound and it stopped bleeding.

408
00:35:37,775 --> 00:35:39,823
He passed out in the beginning because

409
00:35:39,897 --> 00:35:42,364
he was terrified and stressed out.

410
00:35:43,321 --> 00:35:44,322
Excuse me.

411
00:36:02,244 --> 00:36:03,245
Phob.

412
00:36:03,556 --> 00:36:05,564
Phob, don't leave me.

413
00:36:06,063 --> 00:36:08,404
- Your Highness?
- Phob, don't go.

414
00:36:09,484 --> 00:36:10,485
Your Highness.

415
00:36:11,274 --> 00:36:13,724
I'm here. I'm right here.

416
00:36:15,924 --> 00:36:16,925
I'm right here with you.

417
00:36:25,340 --> 00:36:26,341
It's fine.

418
00:36:27,186 --> 00:36:28,187
It's going to be okay.

419
00:36:29,604 --> 00:36:31,324
Your Phob is right here with you.

420
00:36:33,264 --> 00:36:34,804
And I won't leave your side, ever.

421
00:37:02,204 --> 00:37:05,124
Dad, I don't think we should report
a missing person to the police.

422
00:37:05,228 --> 00:37:07,388
Tin will come back soon.
He might get drunk somewhere.

423
00:37:07,426 --> 00:37:09,429
Tinnakorn is not like you.

424
00:37:09,444 --> 00:37:11,084
He won't get too drunk to go home.

425
00:37:11,119 --> 00:37:13,124
Something must've happened to him.

426
00:37:17,898 --> 00:37:18,899
Phob?

427
00:37:23,852 --> 00:37:25,244
You should go.

428
00:37:25,335 --> 00:37:27,164
I'm fine.

429
00:37:27,844 --> 00:37:28,845
Tinnakorn?

430
00:37:29,466 --> 00:37:30,467
What happened to you?

431
00:37:34,201 --> 00:37:36,164
- What did you do?
- Dad!

432
00:37:36,404 --> 00:37:38,764
- What did you do to my son?
- Please, no.

433
00:37:39,578 --> 00:37:41,364
Please, don't hurt him.

434
00:37:41,684 --> 00:37:42,685
No! Dad!

435
00:37:43,044 --> 00:37:44,045
Dad!

436
00:37:44,344 --> 00:37:46,204
Why don't you ask your other son?

437
00:37:46,345 --> 00:37:48,804
Who really hurt Prince Tinnakorn?

438
00:37:50,340 --> 00:37:51,604
Phob! You shut up!

439
00:37:53,322 --> 00:37:55,244
Chat? What is going on?

440
00:37:59,524 --> 00:38:00,804
I got ambushed yesterday,

441
00:38:03,204 --> 00:38:05,485
Prince Tinnakorn saw it
so he shieled me from the bullet.

442
00:38:05,956 --> 00:38:07,284
He saved my life.

443
00:38:15,724 --> 00:38:16,725
You did that?

444
00:38:18,586 --> 00:38:19,587
Huh?

445
00:38:19,764 --> 00:38:23,284
Chat? Did you try to kill him?

446
00:38:24,223 --> 00:38:26,364
He is lying, don't believe him.

447
00:38:26,410 --> 00:38:27,944
You're still denying it even now?

448
00:38:28,564 --> 00:38:30,124
This is so typical of you,

449
00:38:30,404 --> 00:38:32,364
you're such a coward, so useless.

450
00:38:32,415 --> 00:38:33,566
Phob! You slave!

451
00:38:34,367 --> 00:38:35,964
What is going on?

452
00:38:36,404 --> 00:38:39,244
You two used to live together.

453
00:38:42,322 --> 00:38:43,612
I'm sorry, Your Highness,

454
00:38:43,756 --> 00:38:45,244
for causing you some troubles.

455
00:38:47,364 --> 00:38:48,484
I should get going.

456
00:39:11,919 --> 00:39:13,484
What the hell did you do?

457
00:39:14,604 --> 00:39:16,084
Can't you just stay still?

458
00:39:16,799 --> 00:39:18,444
You want to go to jail?

459
00:39:19,290 --> 00:39:20,431
Have you ever thought that

460
00:39:20,663 --> 00:39:23,324
if Phob went to the police,
what effect will it have on me?

461
00:39:24,804 --> 00:39:26,805
He attacked me first.

462
00:39:29,004 --> 00:39:30,724
He told his guys to hurt me.

463
00:39:31,161 --> 00:39:32,804
You expected me to do nothing?

464
00:39:33,484 --> 00:39:36,644
And let that slave stomp
on my face for free?

465
00:39:37,364 --> 00:39:39,004
If you hadn't come to him first,

466
00:39:39,495 --> 00:39:41,096
if you hadn't hurt his mom,

467
00:39:41,124 --> 00:39:42,724
he wouldn't have attacked you like that.

468
00:39:43,444 --> 00:39:44,964
You are always causing troubles.

469
00:39:45,484 --> 00:39:47,766
You are always ruining
the family's reputation.

470
00:39:48,794 --> 00:39:50,764
Why are you blaming me?

471
00:39:54,044 --> 00:39:55,764
I did all of that

472
00:39:56,762 --> 00:39:58,756
to teach them some lessons.

473
00:39:59,430 --> 00:40:01,750
So he would be scared and stop
the plan to transform the nation

474
00:40:01,774 --> 00:40:03,654
and transform the royal
family members like us.

475
00:40:07,039 --> 00:40:09,884
You've never seen anything good in me.

476
00:40:11,804 --> 00:40:14,204
I have never seen it because you have none!

477
00:40:14,805 --> 00:40:15,806
Chat!

478
00:40:16,294 --> 00:40:19,284
You are so useless to me!

479
00:40:21,295 --> 00:40:22,684
You're such a disgrace to me.

480
00:40:22,970 --> 00:40:24,244
You're so full of troubles.

481
00:40:26,971 --> 00:40:29,084
What had I done so wrong in my past lives?

482
00:40:29,156 --> 00:40:30,524
Why do I have you as a son?

483
00:40:32,624 --> 00:40:34,154
If I only had Tinnakorn as my only child,

484
00:40:34,178 --> 00:40:36,764
I wouldn't have had any bad headaches
for the rest of my life.

485
00:41:04,052 --> 00:41:06,084
What is going on?

486
00:41:06,922 --> 00:41:11,044
Why did Chat become such a cruel person?

487
00:41:11,962 --> 00:41:13,084
I wonder the same thing.

488
00:41:13,407 --> 00:41:15,564
Prince Chatthorn never liked Phob.

489
00:41:15,988 --> 00:41:18,404
But I don't think he would
hate him enough to kill Phob.

490
00:41:19,652 --> 00:41:21,405
It was more than that.

491
00:41:22,604 --> 00:41:24,164
Did you see Vasin

492
00:41:25,663 --> 00:41:28,004
and his reaction to Phob?

493
00:41:29,423 --> 00:41:32,780
They acted as if they were
enemies for such a long time.

494
00:41:33,316 --> 00:41:35,084
In the past,

495
00:41:35,691 --> 00:41:37,564
Vasin adored Phob.

496
00:41:38,164 --> 00:41:40,204
And Phob

497
00:41:41,084 --> 00:41:43,744
used to respect Vasin so much.

498
00:41:46,967 --> 00:41:48,044
Your Highness?

499
00:41:48,677 --> 00:41:50,757
Before Phob left the palace.

500
00:41:51,344 --> 00:41:54,644
Prince Chatthorn said that
Phob sneaked in to see Prince Tinnakorn.

501
00:41:55,844 --> 00:41:57,144
After that,

502
00:41:57,915 --> 00:42:02,044
Prince Vasin forbade us
from mentioning Phob.

503
00:42:03,084 --> 00:42:04,804
Do you think it could be related?

504
00:42:19,554 --> 00:42:20,555
How are you feeling?

505
00:42:22,028 --> 00:42:24,544
I'm fine, just a scratch on my arm.

506
00:42:35,029 --> 00:42:37,164
Why did you have to
risk your life like that?

507
00:42:39,788 --> 00:42:41,764
I tried to protect Chat,

508
00:42:42,383 --> 00:42:44,044
protect our family.

509
00:42:45,294 --> 00:42:46,884
If something had happened to Phob,

510
00:42:47,123 --> 00:42:48,563
Chat would have been in big trouble.

511
00:42:50,751 --> 00:42:51,764
Are you sure about that?

512
00:42:54,712 --> 00:42:56,917
It wasn't because you
still have feelings for him?

513
00:42:58,180 --> 00:42:59,964
And you would die to protect him?

514
00:43:05,284 --> 00:43:06,564
My feelings

515
00:43:07,085 --> 00:43:09,286
don't really matter here.

516
00:43:12,364 --> 00:43:14,404
When the celebration is over,

517
00:43:16,063 --> 00:43:19,516
Phob and I won't see each other again.

518
00:43:30,964 --> 00:43:33,484
Then I should leave you to rest.

519
00:43:35,447 --> 00:43:36,448
Dad?

520
00:43:41,596 --> 00:43:43,964
The celebration went
smoothly and nothing happened.

521
00:43:45,393 --> 00:43:47,494
It meant that Phob had nothing to do with

522
00:43:47,604 --> 00:43:49,204
the regime change's team.

523
00:43:51,383 --> 00:43:52,764
Can I ask you

524
00:43:53,703 --> 00:43:54,944
to leave Phob alone?

525
00:43:55,527 --> 00:43:56,764
Stop monitoring him.

526
00:43:57,143 --> 00:43:59,204
We also should stop messing with him.

527
00:44:00,887 --> 00:44:02,327
We won't be in touch with him again.

528
00:44:03,644 --> 00:44:05,324
Can you do that for me?

529
00:44:38,460 --> 00:44:41,020
Fortunately, we didn't start our mission
during the celebration.

530
00:44:41,684 --> 00:44:44,804
Otherwise, it would've been a
bloodbath of an uprising for sure.

531
00:44:46,861 --> 00:44:48,884
We can't sit on it for too long.

532
00:44:49,196 --> 00:44:51,684
The longer we wait,
the longer we give them time to plan.

533
00:44:54,384 --> 00:44:57,185
I think we should take more time.

534
00:44:59,074 --> 00:45:01,570
We need to think and plan carefully.

535
00:45:02,084 --> 00:45:04,124
We still need information from all sources.

536
00:45:05,591 --> 00:45:06,764
Especially from you,

537
00:45:07,084 --> 00:45:08,085
Phobthee.

538
00:45:09,556 --> 00:45:11,804
You need to be around Prince Tinnakorn.

539
00:45:12,266 --> 00:45:14,844
The schedule from the royal
secretary was useful to us.

540
00:45:17,350 --> 00:45:18,870
But the celebration is over.

541
00:45:19,930 --> 00:45:22,090
I don't think our path will cross again.

542
00:45:23,597 --> 00:45:26,677
Don't worry about your path with him.

543
00:45:27,544 --> 00:45:28,684
Give me a month,

544
00:45:29,724 --> 00:45:31,484
I will find a way to send you

545
00:45:31,924 --> 00:45:33,844
to work with Prince Tinnakorn

546
00:45:34,004 --> 00:45:35,804
in the Royal Palace Office again.

547
00:45:57,036 --> 00:45:59,756
You feel bad for having to
lie to Prince Tinnakorn again, don't you?

548
00:46:08,946 --> 00:46:10,028
During the celebration,

549
00:46:12,300 --> 00:46:14,644
- Prince Chatthorn tried to shoot me.
- What?

550
00:46:15,506 --> 00:46:16,724
Are you okay?

551
00:46:20,908 --> 00:46:21,909
Phob!

552
00:46:25,756 --> 00:46:27,364
Prince Tinnakorn was there to save me.

553
00:46:29,719 --> 00:46:31,564
He took a bullet for me.

554
00:46:34,508 --> 00:46:35,509
Janthorn.

555
00:46:37,612 --> 00:46:38,724
He saved my life.

556
00:46:41,612 --> 00:46:43,164
And now I have to use him again.

557
00:46:45,804 --> 00:46:46,844
I know

558
00:46:47,643 --> 00:46:50,363
- that you two were so close.
- Janthorn.

559
00:46:54,143 --> 00:46:56,484
I am so grateful for Prince Tinnakorn.

560
00:47:01,285 --> 00:47:03,925
He has never looked down on me
even though I was only his servant.

561
00:47:07,281 --> 00:47:09,484
He made my life in the palace

562
00:47:10,644 --> 00:47:11,804
so happy and peaceful

563
00:47:16,354 --> 00:47:17,724
from his kindness.

564
00:47:23,474 --> 00:47:24,924
Look what I have to repay him,

565
00:47:26,820 --> 00:47:27,844
I'm a traitor.

566
00:47:29,076 --> 00:47:31,524
I betrayed him and I used him.

567
00:47:46,274 --> 00:47:47,275
Phob, listen to me.

568
00:47:48,812 --> 00:47:50,772
I understand that we put
you in a tough position.

569
00:47:52,700 --> 00:47:54,524
But what we are doing right now

570
00:47:55,060 --> 00:47:56,544
is nothing personal.

571
00:47:58,472 --> 00:48:00,957
We are trying to transform the nation.

572
00:48:02,399 --> 00:48:03,879
We are doing this for people's rights

573
00:48:04,535 --> 00:48:06,882
and their freedom.

574
00:48:10,482 --> 00:48:11,684
- But I…
- Listen to me,

575
00:48:14,450 --> 00:48:16,204
about the royal family's schedule,

576
00:48:17,362 --> 00:48:19,684
I will ask my sources to look for it.

577
00:48:20,812 --> 00:48:22,172
If we can get one from my sources,

578
00:48:22,332 --> 00:48:24,532
you don't have to get
anything out of Prince Tinnakorn.

579
00:48:27,703 --> 00:48:29,044
But if I can't get one,

580
00:48:31,404 --> 00:48:32,605
we need to rely on you.

581
00:48:42,580 --> 00:48:44,604
If he knows what we are doing,

582
00:48:47,647 --> 00:48:49,244
he will hate me for sure.

583
00:48:52,719 --> 00:48:54,124
You said it yourself

584
00:48:55,119 --> 00:48:57,324
that he has never looked down on anyone.

585
00:48:58,586 --> 00:49:00,804
He is a man with great vision.

586
00:49:02,000 --> 00:49:03,757
I believe that when the day comes,

587
00:49:04,860 --> 00:49:08,284
he will understand and forgive you.

588
00:49:22,860 --> 00:49:25,380
The archives for 150th anniversary
of Rattanakosin celebration?

589
00:49:26,167 --> 00:49:27,168
Yes, Your Highness.

590
00:49:27,996 --> 00:49:30,964
The army sent me to work
with the royal secretary department

591
00:49:31,772 --> 00:49:34,044
so that the archives will
be accurate and complete.

592
00:49:38,247 --> 00:49:39,324
How is your wound?

593
00:49:41,866 --> 00:49:42,867
I feel so much better.

594
00:49:46,047 --> 00:49:49,444
But it's been only a month.

595
00:49:53,242 --> 00:49:54,243
And…

596
00:49:55,002 --> 00:49:57,724
many royal family members
are staying in Hua Hin, aren't they?

597
00:49:59,311 --> 00:50:01,231
I don't think there is
anything urgent going on.

598
00:50:01,823 --> 00:50:03,263
You should have taken more days off.

599
00:50:03,668 --> 00:50:05,394
Even if they are not staying in the city,

600
00:50:06,260 --> 00:50:09,100
there are still papers from various
ministries that I need to care for.

601
00:50:11,065 --> 00:50:12,066
You're right.

602
00:50:15,876 --> 00:50:19,434
When are they coming back to the city?

603
00:50:20,852 --> 00:50:23,326
Are they staying at Klai
Kangwong Palace for long?

604
00:50:25,164 --> 00:50:26,524
Why do you want to know?

605
00:50:33,431 --> 00:50:34,924
I should know their exact schedule

606
00:50:35,714 --> 00:50:38,724
so I can hurry up with the
archives when they return.

607
00:50:39,831 --> 00:50:42,151
This way, I don't have to disturb you
when you're working.

608
00:50:52,908 --> 00:50:54,084
Captain Phobthee?

609
00:50:54,946 --> 00:50:57,164
Why are you here for?

610
00:51:05,429 --> 00:51:08,004
The prince and I are not strangers.

611
00:51:08,535 --> 00:51:10,215
I don’t have to visit him because of work,

612
00:51:10,935 --> 00:51:14,004
perhaps I can visit him when I miss him.

613
00:51:14,359 --> 00:51:15,484
The army sent

614
00:51:15,634 --> 00:51:17,244
him to work with me

615
00:51:17,335 --> 00:51:19,164
about the celebration's archives, Dad.

616
00:51:42,400 --> 00:51:43,500
(Next Episode)
Go back.

617
00:51:45,400 --> 00:51:48,599
Go back! Go back! Go away!

618
00:51:48,600 --> 00:51:50,500
Why can't I ever escape this?

619
00:51:50,600 --> 00:51:52,876
Now that you've returned like this,
what do you want me to do?

620
00:51:52,900 --> 00:51:55,300
How do you expect me to forget you?

621
00:52:02,900 --> 00:52:05,199
A spy reported that
two of our soldiers have been captured.

622
00:52:05,200 --> 00:52:06,999
The list of those involved
in the movement will surely leak.

623
00:52:07,000 --> 00:52:09,400
We must take action to
change the country very soon.

624
00:52:21,076 --> 00:52:23,876
[Official notice the King will move
to Klai Kang Won Palace in HuaHin.]
